Eevee (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0132: Ditto
Pokémon
#0134: Vaporeon →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Eevee (TCG Pocket).

Eevee has been featured on 69 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Eevee cards are normally Colorless-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Eevee

Eevee
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
